.\"\n\n\"Cash on hand increased to $26.2 million as of April 23, 2026, up from $12.8 million at year-end 2025, which we estimate provides us with at least a 12-month runway.\"\n\n\"The next orbital service vehicle mission, planned for 2027, is fully subscribed with NASA-awarded contracts, demonstrating continued customer demand.\"", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 4, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 29, "quoteCount": 1, "viewCount": 5190, "createdAt": "Tue May 05 12:08:19 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 6, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051635097078489359", "displayTextRange": [0, 280], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "SpaceInvestor_D", "url": "https://x.com/SpaceInvestor_D", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/SpaceInvestor_D", "id": "1505909833190592519", "name": "Space Investor", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1951359577489854464/iDXt_yJ-_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1505909833190592519/1735589960", "description": "", "location": "No Financial Advice", "followers": 48647, "following": 1886, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Mon Mar 21 14:11:14 +0000 2022", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 59714, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 4052, "statusesCount": 16947, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2051027601427157289"], "profile_bio": {"description": "Ex market maker. Now Investing in the final frontier. Subscribe for more \u2935\ufe0f", "entities": {"description": {}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "tinyurl.com/43ej9j7d", "expanded_url": "http://tinyurl.com/43ej9j7d", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/JrzqZ6kJlN"}]}}}, "isAu